---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Thank You for Subscribing"
  description="Thank you for subscribing to the 757tech newsletter."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Subscribed</h1>
    <p>Thanks for joining the 757tech newsletter. You'll now receive:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Weekly updates on tech events, meetups, and happenings across Hampton Roads.</li>
      <li>Early access and offers for major events like Hampton Roads DevFest and RevolutionConf.</li>
      <li>Opportunities to volunteer and contribute to the community.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Your first update is on its way.</p>
    <p>
      In the meantime: <a href="/">back to home</a> &middot; <a href="/calendar">view the calendar</a> &middot; <a href="/get-involved">get involved</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
